 \"the highly rated Belgians\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"the semi\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 883}, {\"ngram\": \"finals\", \"from\": 884, \"to\": 890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The finalists will go straight to the Olympics, and they will be joined by the winner of the third place play-off.\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 1007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The finalists\", \"from\": 893, \"to\": 906}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 927, \"to\": 939}, {\"ngram\": \"the winner\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 978}, {\"ngram\": \"the third place play-off\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 1006}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We'd be confident we can get the group off to a good start with a win against Ukraine,\\\" said Murray.\", \"from\": 1009, \"to\": 1110, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1095, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999882973050184, \"rank\": 8.978654434423031e-06, \"text\": \"Ukraine\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1103, \"end\": 1109, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999815827, \"rank\": 1.8387077829177355e-11, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the group\", \"from\": 1039, \"to\": 1048}, {\"ngram\": \"a good start\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1068}, {\"ngram\": \"a win\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Japan, we do not know too much about, [so] we will treat the Japan game as a must-win game.\", \"from\": 1112, \"to\": 1204, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1174, \"end\": 1179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999918525502322, \"rank\": 8.029355593027453e-06, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a must-win game\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1203}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We know that they are experienced.\", \"from\": 1205, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And Belgium are the favourites, but we know that we can get at them,\\\" said Murray, who plays his club hockey in the Belgian league with Gantoise.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1246, \"end\": 1253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999976647659405, \"rank\": 2.3305919039212497e-06, \"text\": \"Belgium\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1317, \"end\": 1323, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999815827, \"rank\": 1.8387077829177355e-11, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}, {\"begin\": 1358, \"end\": 1365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999990949269889, \"rank\": 9.040181398763156e-07, \"text\": \"Belgian\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belgium_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/La_Gantoise_HC\", \"scor