we love it,\\\" said Murray.\", \"from\": 1843, \"to\": 1931, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 0.9999999999815827, \"rank\": 1.8387077829177355e-11, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The underdog mentality\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"an Irishman\", \"from\": 1871, \"to\": 1882}, {\"ngram\": \"the squad\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1904}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have done it lots of times in the past when we have been out for the count, and come back and succeeded.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 1950, \"to\": 1954}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 1958, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 1967, \"to\": 1975}, {\"ngram\": \"the count\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2011}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So hopefully we can use that, and if it comes down to the dying minutes, we can use that and we will have confidence in ourselves.\\\"\", \"from\": 2043, \"to\": 2175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dying minutes\", \"from\": 2098, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"confidence\", \"from\": 2150, \"to\": 2160}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The squad leave for Spain on Sunday ahead of the qualification tournament and will be motivated to go one step futher than last time out when they narrowly missed out on Tokyo 2020 qualification by the narrowest of margins in Canada four years ago.\", \"from\": 2177, \"to\": 2425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999986721377, \"rank\": 1.3205520643138958e-09, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"ht